    "trained a similar model for screening A. baumannii antibiotic candidates using a dataset of 7684 experimentally tested molecules (ROC 0.792) 4, 5, 91.",
    "They also applied this model to a set of drug repurposing candidates and reported 40 out of 240 empirically validated molecules showed >80% growth inhibition.",
    "In summary, this technique can reduce screening time compared to traditional high-throughput screening and is especially useful for drug repurposing.",
    "In order to discover new generative deep learning models have been increasingly employed in the past years.",
